“Update mkdocs.yml nav to remove all curriculum/* entries since docs/curriculum was deleted; keep only Governance and Professional Development (Grit & Growth Mindset student + instructor). Update docs/index.md PDF link to the full GitHub Pages URL so MkDocs doesn’t warn about missing internal targets. After warnings are gone, set strict: true.”

That’s it. This gets you back to a clean build and makes the repo ready for the next uploads without dragging the old placeholder junk around.

