# ANEW Curriculum Master

This repository is the single source of truth for curriculum content and hour enforcement.

## Key links

- Governance (how changes are controlled and reviewed)
  - Single Source of Truth
  - Pull Request Workflow
  - Golden Rule Enforcement
  - Change Control

- Professional Development
  - Grit & Growth Mindset (Student)
  - Grit & Growth Mindset (Instructor)

## Curriculum PDF

The PDF is generated during production builds and published here:

https://mandy1eigh007.github.io/curriculum_master/downloads/curriculum.pdf
