You’re good. Here’s what you should have Copilot do next (and you can paste this straight in), because right now your repo is still pointing MkDocs navigation at files you deleted (docs/curriculum/**). That’s why you’re seeing all the “nav configuration … not found” warnings.

What you need Copilot to fix
Update mkdocs.yml nav to remove all curriculum/... entries (since you deleted docs/curriculum/).

